html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-2111369919636382v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by jayneconverse3", "description": "Part 2: They’re not following Trump because of what he does. They’re following him because of how he makes them feel. This isn’t just politics—it’s identity, rage, and emotional manipulation. Understanding it is the first step in breaking the spell.\n\n#trumpcult #authoritarianism #politicalpsychology #cultofpersonality \n#resistfascism #truthmatters #defenddemocracy #wakeupamerica", "duration": 180.0, "timestamp": 1751161129, "uploader_id": "45123321307", "uploader": "Jayne Converse", "channel": "jayneconverse3", "like_count": 38838, "comment_count": 230, "comments": [{"author": "dalarsenojai", "author_id": "9840144352", "id": "17874469041459463", "text": "It's called fucking brainwashing", "timestamp": 1765469258}, {"author": "greg_ukguy", "author_id": "1572763619", "id": "17891129007245346", "text": "It’s like when they say “he’s a great businessman?” He bankrupted a casino, airline, liquor brand and a meat producing business. Great skills", "timestamp": 1764324201}, {"author": "dancinglita", "author_id": "582532372", "id": "18132549283493052", "text": "Let’s do it. Thank you for this message. Makes alot of sense.", "timestamp": 1764001651}, {"author": "60butno1toldme", "author_id": "30279504419", "id": "17851322172592899", "text": "You need to grow your platform dramatically and increase the scope of your voice.", "timestamp": 1763911255}, {"author": "grizzlysandbear", "author_id": "9448998137", "id": "18101234848751560", "text": "In addition, I would add that the conditioning regarding labeling the opposition as truly evil and unworthy leads many to ignore and dismiss anything the opposition says.", "timestamp": 1763747407}, {"author": "connie_rae_pederson", "author_id": "39480618251", "id": "18320331433173875", "text": "Exactly right, these are our families, friends, colleagues and we need to figure it out.", "timestamp": 1763731301}, {"author": "rwilso8", "author_id": "206883298", "id": "18082120550037308", "text": "I wish we were friends!  I love your content", "timestamp": 1763649481}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/504342907_1057225732655892_8183932768258036490_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHOl-RSY3jnPWCzZlxhU6lLqE77QYRrSgxIzBFY9SbW43Gu1nIwOPWf940nHPnVcuA&_nc_ohc=7pWSSwI6OR8Q7kNvwHxamVh&_nc_gid=ZHZUbIEyfy4I2NYQM0BIXQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0-44Ubx9AkIcTi5f7lXkpoKYFwjbBkcFWWWeHGF2MnOA&oe=69D4CF9D&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/504342907_1057225732655892_8183932768258036490_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHOl-RSY3jnPWCzZlxhU6lLqE77QYRrSgxIzBFY9SbW43Gu1nIwOPWf940nHPnVcuA&_nc_ohc=7pWSSwI6OR8Q7kNvwHxamVh&_nc_gid=ZHZUbIEyfy4I2NYQM0BIXQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0-44Ubx9AkIcTi5f7lXkpoKYFwjbBkcFWWWeHGF2MnOA&oe=69D4CF9D&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/504342907_1057225732655892_8183932768258036490_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHOl-RSY3jnPWCzZlxhU6lLqE77QYRrSgxIzBFY9SbW43Gu1nIwOPWf940nHPnVcuA&_nc_ohc=7pWSSwI6OR8Q7kNvwHxamVh&_nc_gid=ZHZUbIEyfy4I2NYQM0BIXQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=